<span id="freeTextContainer13705853548875262836">Whilst I admit that there are some shrewdly observed elements of a fractured relationship (unfortunately writing from experience), this is not a pleasant read at all. It begins as it means to go on... and on... and on...<br/><br/>I had enough of a struggle making sense of my own disaster without looking on in Peeping Tom fashion at someone else&apos;s</span>
